::Magmatron::

    Using a fusion cutter he started to slice a hole in the ship. It barely 
goes through though. So he turns up the beam and begins again. Cutting into 
the ship is hard enough but he is doing it at sea level so he has to deal 
with the waves.
    Suddenly his head jerks toward the sky. He abonandons attacking the ship. 
    "Destrons, this is Magmatron, do not engage the Iron Fist, I repeat, do 
not engage," Magmatron said into his comm heading back to the Destron base.
